thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Vicky & Michael

author: Vicky & Michael
title: Vicky & Michael
text: Truc assisted us in the search of our investment property and went above and beyond her role. She would communicate with us regularly, take us through opens during her work and non work hours and was honest in all her dealings with us. Truc has extensive knowledge in the real estate industry and her people's skills are second to none. We cannot thank you enough Truc.
